{"word":"ἰχθυβόλος","slug":"ἰχθυβόλος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἰχθυβόλος</b></el> <el>(ἰχθυ-βόλος, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:βάλλω'><el>βάλλω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>striking fish</i>, <el>ἰχθ. μηχανή</el>, of the trident, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>as <a href='S:Substantive'>Subst.</a> <i>a fisher, angler</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a>, <el>ἰχθ. θήρα</el> a spoil <i>of speared fish</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}